{"3875970": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Is this Really a Massage!?", "steam_appid": 3875970, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您精湛的球技會讓她愛上您，愛上您的身體和靈魂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作簡單。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要用滑鼠拖曳黏糊糊的 Live2D 角色即可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/7eb8fcfd5b826e166fec0d73477e6d8c.poster.avif?t=1776577850\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/7eb8fcfd5b826e166fec0d73477e6d8c.webm?t=1776577850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/7eb8fcfd5b826e166fec0d73477e6d8c.mp4?t=1776577850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著遊戲的進行，她會放輕鬆，並將自己交給快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/82c2ed81ccc4a5f5f686a1e95ab6d360.poster.avif?t=1776577850\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/82c2ed81ccc4a5f5f686a1e95ab6d360.webm?t=1776577850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/82c2ed81ccc4a5f5f686a1e95ab6d360.mp4?t=1776577850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*PV 中的聲音是暫時的。在上映時，獨家配音將為全新拍攝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/d045d22f9cb2d8d3200542cdffc32732.poster.avif?t=1776577850\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/d045d22f9cb2d8d3200542cdffc32732.webm?t=1776577850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/d045d22f9cb2d8d3200542cdffc32732.mp4?t=1776577850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲系統</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整的 Live2D 動畫！您可以拖曳身體的各個部位，例如頭部、胸部和大腿。您可以根據拖曳的部位和拖曳的移動方式給予各種刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您拖曳的速度以及垂直和水平移動的組合會改變她的感覺，因此請嘗試不同的方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她會即時對您的每個動作做出反應，並播放調皮的動畫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她的反應、呼吸和音效與您的滑鼠移動完全同步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>配備情感引擎</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她的面部表情會根據三個參數自動變化：不耐煩、快感和強度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您突然猛烈地移動她，她會感到更多的刺激而不是快感，並且會更加扭動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一開始您應該可以輕輕地感覺到，等您習慣了之後，即使激烈地玩也可以感覺到。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/a023036993ea80cbf37d17612ed79030.poster.avif?t=1776577850\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/a023036993ea80cbf37d17612ed79030.webm?t=1776577850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3875970/extras/a023036993ea80cbf37d17612ed79030.mp4?t=1776577850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您精湛的球技會讓她愛上您，愛上您的身體和靈魂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作簡單。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要用滑鼠拖曳黏糊糊的 Live2D 角色即可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.